# managedObjectModel

**Instance Property**

The container’s managed object model.

## Declaration

```swift
var managedObjectModel: NSManagedObjectModel { get }
```

## Discussion

This property contains a reference to the [doc://com.apple.coredata/documentation/CoreData/NSManagedObjectModel] object associated with this persistent container.

## Getting the Container’s Configuration

- **name**: The container’s name.
- **persistentStoreCoordinator**: The container’s persistent store coordinator.
